  m_text: "<color=#4fffe2>@beepbeepwithmustache: name plr char Cross\n@neil.sanchez4:
    big terry\n@treyten_fr: big terry (but louder)\n@dariusz_50: Big terry (but even
    louder)\n@gubby836: big Terry (but very very louder)\n@riss.2222: name the player
    char Jon the 3</color>\n@3m_isme: me.\n<color=#4fffe2>@theonlyaluca: name the
    plr char bird\n@luisjimenezmoreno_tito: name the plr char jimster \n@GringusMingus:
    add a potato shaped shark with a cowboy hat named Mogi</color>\n@flamgowas_taken:
    customizable flag on the cape\n@eggza6: add this guy <color=#9f9f9f>*weird deer
    image*</color>\n@limitedliel: Make the gull's hat bigger\n@derpyxb: add a minesweeper
    boss\n@36_lenore_63: a flying TV head named karlson\n@pangula75: little cartoon
    jester that chucks bombs at sandcastle\n@average_poker_player: make little ravens/crows
    that pay you for killing bossess\n@grimmking0: mirror of george who gets beaten
    with a monolouge based on Wurthering Heights"
