      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '@Picklenuggys: If you press the letter G the screen has a pickle

    @Puma_202:
    special currency the rat gives that you can spend on an item shop

    @kidontheinternet8107:
    Make TheMan give you cheese tokens that you can use to buy upgrades

    @Deadfish9:
    when enemies die they turn into a red mist

    @Armedfatrat: a rat png rarely
    appears after you kill an enemy

    @highlord2841: dark souls boss fight

    @LVKEdoesGames:
    0.5% chance for an enemy to run away

    @Nove277: ninja enemy that is kinda
    hidden

    @Jack70clips: God mode locked and a god mode where you can activate
    it

    @Darthtreder: ricochet bullet

    @Slomiboy: green circle that gives
    you a buff when you destroy it

    @Blueshark_1567: watermelon enemy named blooping
    that attacks 3x in a row

    @JMan-f4h: battle royale mode

    @6Versy6: animal
    only mode

    @rerhaha9344: tornado gun that summons tornado, fire, and small
    chance of pets

    @bob-d2u2c: big purple man comes from sun if reached wave
    50 or 100 but if not gives 3CT

    @parkerthompson: add an AK or sniper

    @GrassStone:
    add a main menu'
